{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said, if I would have a car, I would go, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so she came, and she went with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And tell me, just before we go on with that-- and I want to get on with that-- can you tell me a bit more about your brothers and sisters?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One-- one brother-- What, from '39?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the youngest in the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really don't remember too much about them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I don't like to say something that I really don't remember it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All I can say, I-- I was the baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was very secure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very secure, because we were quite well off, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was secure in every way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't missing on anything when I was a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always could get a few-- there were zlotys in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I-- I always had a few zlotys with me, to go to school, to buy things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I never missed anything as a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was the youngest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was spoiled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I played with the other children, outside, not with my brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The youngest sister, yes, but not with the others anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had a menswear-- a menswear store and a liquor restaurant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were two separate business, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were involved in it, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were two brothers, yes, and there was an elder sister, as well, the eldest sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the brothers were involved in it, more than anything, with the parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, on the-- on the first night, when the war broke out, as I said before, we tried to get a car to get away from the city.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
